 As lock-down restrictions begin to ease around the world, the small pleasures in life are returning to normality such as beauty salons, leisure travel and now movie theatres. Nu Metro has announced its reopening its flagship cinema complexes this month with a many safety precautions in place to ensure that the entertainment industry can survive this pandemic. Joining CNBC Africa for more is Chantelle Burrows, Marketing & Content Executive for Nu Metro Cinemas.